# Catalog Entry Template

Copy this file, rename to olht-XXXX.md, and fill in. One file per archive item. The fields mirror the JSON schema in METADATA_SCHEMA.md.

Fields marked *[required]* must be filled before the item is ingested. Fields marked *[community]* must be filled or confirmed by a community reviewer before the item moves out of the holding tier.

